description:
Here are two evenly matched opponents, both with limited mat
experience, both without a win to date. Both hate losing, and both
want their first win. This match went back and forth at times, but when
it was all said and done, Tony's superior strength was the deciding
factor. Dana DeArmond will have to wait to get her first win.
title: The Jester (0-2) Tony (0-1)
